PN,30701
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1780625006
OL,3,CNew AI-designed vaccine 'could protect
OL,4,Cagainst whole families of viruses'
OL,6,FNew vaccine technology created with
OL,7,Fthe help of artificial intelligence
OL,8,Fcould provide immunity against whole
OL,9,Ffamilies of viruses and protect people
OL,10,Ffrom any future mutations in a single
OL,11,Fjab, according to scientists.
OL,13,FThe method could prevent pandemics
OL,14,Fbefore they begin, saving millions of
OL,15,Flives and helping countries avoid
OL,16,Flockdowns, researchers said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1780625006
OL,3,CNew AI-designed vaccine 'could protect
OL,4,Cagainst whole families of viruses'
OL,6,FThe "super-antigen" is developed by
OL,7,Fusing machine learning that analyses
OL,8,Fpast and current outbreaks to
OL,9,Fdetermine what is essential for
OL,10,Fviruses to survive.
OL,12,FA world-first human trial has shown
OL,13,Fthat a coronavirus vaccine made using
OL,14,Fthe technology is safe, with more than
OL,15,F200 people set to be recruited for a
OL,16,Fphase II study.
OL,18,FExperts hailed the method as a "big
OL,19,Fparadigm change" to the current
OL,20,F"reactive" system which "struggles to
OL,21,Fkeep pace" as diseases evolve.
OL,26,@nD@EOUnD@SO]zD@`OU{D@PO]|D@AOU|D@JO]|D@
OL,26,AYOU}D@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1780625006
OL,3,CNew AI-designed vaccine 'could protect
OL,4,Cagainst whole families of viruses'
OL,6,FCurrent vaccines use antigens from
OL,7,Fspecific strains of virus that have
OL,8,Falready been detected in humans.
OL,10,FHowever, the universal Sarbeco
OL,11,Fcoronavirus vaccine, developed by the
OL,12,FUniversity of Cambridge and
OL,13,Fbiotechnology company DIOSynVax,
OL,14,Fbrings together features that are
OL,15,Fcommon in the whole family of viruses.
OL,17,FThis is done by researchers taking all
OL,18,Favailable genetic sequence data on
OL,19,Fcoronaviruses logged by surveillance
OL,20,Fprogrammes around the world to create
OL,21,Fa "super antigen".
OL,26,@}D@COU}D@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1780625006
OL,3,CNew AI-designed vaccine 'could protect
OL,4,Cagainst whole families of viruses'
OL,6,FProfessor Jonathan Heeney, from the
OL,7,Flab of viral zoonotics at the
OL,8,FUniversity of Cambridge's Department
OL,9,Fof Veterinary Medicine, told the Press
OL,10,FAssociation: "What that Covid pandemic
OL,11,Ftaught us is how fast we can make
OL,12,Fvaccines, but we're still using the
OL,13,Fold paradigm.
OL,15,F"This is about making one vaccine that
OL,16,Fwill get them all based on their
OL,17,Frelationships."
OL,26,@rD@NOUwD@AOUyD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1780625006
OL,3,CNew AI-designed vaccine 'could protect
OL,4,Cagainst whole families of viruses'
OL,6,FHe added: "You hoover up all the
OL,7,Fgenomic sequences; what's known from
OL,8,Faround the world, from past outbreaks
OL,9,Fand current outbreaks, and you do some
OL,10,Fbasic structural science.
OL,12,F"We take all these different
OL,13,Fsequences...and we think, 'OK, what's
OL,14,Fconsistent amongst them, what's not
OL,15,Fchanging, what is essential for their
OL,16,Flife' and that's what we target.
OL,26,@nD@KOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1780625006
OL,3,CNew AI-designed vaccine 'could protect
OL,4,Cagainst whole families of viruses'
OL,6,F"It not only predicts, but it targets
OL,7,Fwhat is essential for that virus
OL,8,Ffamily. We're targeting something in a
OL,9,Fvirus family, which the virus can't
OL,10,Fchange easily."
OL,12,FA phase I trial, published in the
OL,13,FJournal of Infection, included 49
OL,14,Fhealthy volunteers aged between 18 and
OL,15,F50 who had the vaccine in Cambridge
OL,16,Fand Southampton.
OL,18,FIt was administered as DNA vaccine
OL,19,Fthrough a micro fluid jet.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1780625006
OL,3,CNew AI-designed vaccine 'could protect
OL,4,Cagainst whole families of viruses'
OL,6,FThis is a needle-free method that uses
OL,7,Fa high-pressure, hair-thin stream of
OL,8,Fliquid to push vaccine blueprints
OL,9,Fdirectly into skin cells.
OL,11,FResearchers found the jab is safe and
OL,12,Fthat it triggered an immune response
OL,13,Fto not only SARS-CoV-2 and SARS, but
OL,14,Fto related bat viruses that could
OL,15,Fpotentially jump from animals to
OL,16,Fhumans.
OL,18,FA previous study in animals also found
OL,19,Fthe jab sparked a strong immune
OL,20,Fresponse against a range of
OL,21,Fcoronaviruses.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1780625006
OL,3,CNew AI-designed vaccine 'could protect
OL,4,Cagainst whole families of viruses'
OL,6,FA phase II trial is expected to
OL,7,Finclude "upwards of 200 or more
OL,8,Fpeople", Prof Heeney said.
OL,10,FHe is hopeful that the technology can
OL,11,Fbe a "game changer" that makes
OL,12,Fvaccines "far better, broader, and
OL,13,Fgive more robust protection".
OL,15,FIt could provide broad protection from
OL,16,Fthousands of variants of viruses, such
OL,17,Fas ebola.
OL,26,@oD@IOUpD@GO]sD@FOUsD@SO]tD@JOUuD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1780625006
OL,3,CNew AI-designed vaccine 'could protect
OL,4,Cagainst whole families of viruses'
OL,6,FProf Heeney told PA that during his
OL,7,Fcareer he has travelled during
OL,8,Foutbreaks, and the one that "really
OL,9,Fleft a mark" was the West African
OL,10,FEbola epidemic, which lasted from 2013
OL,11,Fto 2016.
OL,13,FThere is currently another epidemic of
OL,14,Febola happening in the Democratic
OL,15,FRepublic of the Congo (DRC) and
OL,16,FUganda, caused by bundibugyo virus.
OL,18,F"There's a lot of viruses out there,
OL,19,Fand once we know them, we start
OL,20,Fchasing them, but we have to change
OL,21,Fthat paradigm," he said.
OL,26,@pD@]OUqD@LO]zD@AOU}D@OO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1780625006
OL,3,CNew AI-designed vaccine 'could protect
OL,4,Cagainst whole families of viruses'
OL,6,F"And that's what this is about, it's
OL,7,Fabout making vaccines that not just
OL,8,Fprotect us from today's viruses, but
OL,9,Fthe ones that haven't yet happened.
OL,11,F"A great example of that is what's
OL,12,Fgoing on now in the DRC. Again, yet
OL,13,Fanother Ebola virus, but it's not the
OL,14,Fsame one, it's from the same family.
OL,15,FDeja vu. We're behind the curve, and
OL,16,Fthese viruses belong to the same
OL,17,Ffamily.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30711
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1780625006
OL,3,CNew AI-designed vaccine 'could protect
OL,4,Cagainst whole families of viruses'
OL,6,F"So, what we're trying to do is to
OL,7,Fmake a vaccine that will protect
OL,8,Fagainst all those different viruses in
OL,9,Fa family, and it's a big paradigm
OL,10,Fchange."
OL,12,FThe team is also looking to advance on
OL,13,Fa vaccine for bird flu, which Prof
OL,14,FHeeney described as a "big global
OL,15,Fthreat".
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@HO]vD@WOUwD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30712
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1780625006
OL,3,CNew AI-designed vaccine 'could protect
OL,4,Cagainst whole families of viruses'
OL,6,FHe said: "This is because this bird
OL,7,Fflu virus is all around the world, on
OL,8,Fmost continents, not only impacting
OL,9,Fbirds, but also mammals and humans,
OL,10,Fand it's even in the food chain in
OL,11,FAmerica, in milk.
OL,13,F"So it's quite a worry, but there's
OL,14,Fdifferent clades, or types of
OL,15,Ffamilies, and there's particular ones
OL,16,Fin south-east Asia that are very
OL,17,Fdifferent, but that have killed people
OL,18,Fin double digits.
OL,26,@nD@JOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30713
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1780625006
OL,3,CNew AI-designed vaccine 'could protect
OL,4,Cagainst whole families of viruses'
OL,6,F"So it's about making sure that our
OL,7,Ftechnology can get whatever is going
OL,8,Fto pop up and protect us, and to get
OL,9,Fahead of that curve, instead of
OL,10,Fchasing it."
OL,12,FProf Saul Faust, of the University of
OL,13,FSouthampton and the trial's chief
OL,14,Finvestigator, said: "Viruses like
OL,15,Finfluenza, coronaviruses and the ebola
OL,16,Fgroup are evolving continuously and by
OL,17,Fthe time vaccines are rolled out, they
OL,18,Fmay be poorly matched ` the current
OL,19,F'reactive' vaccine system struggles to
OL,20,Fkeep pace.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@LO]vD@UOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30714
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1780625006
OL,3,CNew AI-designed vaccine 'could protect
OL,4,Cagainst whole families of viruses'
OL,6,F"This new class of universal vaccines
OL,7,Fare future-proofed.
OL,9,F"They not only protect against many
OL,10,Fvariants simultaneously, but
OL,11,Fpotentially against related viruses
OL,12,Fthat haven't yet emerged and spilt
OL,13,Fover to humans.
OL,15,F"If we can develop and clinically
OL,16,Fadvance this new class of vaccines
OL,17,Fbefore a virus outbreak begins,
OL,18,Fmillions of lives could be saved,
OL,19,Flockdowns avoided and the economy
OL,20,Fpreserved."
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@AOUwD@AOU|D@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30715
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1780625006
OL,3,CNew AI-designed vaccine 'could protect
OL,4,Cagainst whole families of viruses'
OL,6,FProf Marian Knight, scientific
OL,7,Fdirector for National Institute for
OL,8,FHealth and Care Research (NIHR)
OL,9,FInfrastructure, said: "The remarkable
OL,10,Fsuccess of this AI-designed 'super-
OL,11,Fantigen' trial marks a pivotal leap
OL,12,Fforward in our ability to deliver
OL,13,Fbroad, lasting viral protection."
OL,15,FThe study was sponsored by University
OL,16,FHospital Southampton NHS Foundation
OL,17,FTrust.
OL,26,@qD@WOUuD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/15
